Cyberpunk style: A towering mechanical arm emerging from a neon-lit cloud of swirling data streams, its chrome fingers precisely inserting glowing modular components into a massive floating command terminal. The scene is bathed in electric blue and magenta light, with holographic plugin modules hovering in organized rows like a digital marketplace. Rain-slicked surfaces reflect the vibrant glow of circuit patterns running through everything. In the background, towering server stacks pierce through low-hanging digital clouds, their surfaces covered in pulsing connection ports. The mechanical arm has an industrial yet elegant design, with exposed gears and fiber optic cables running through transparent housing. Small autonomous drones carry additional components through the air, leaving trails of light particles in their wake.
